@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xqhcvf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos((v0 - wp.sin(tmp + 0.80)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v1 + 0.73 * v2 + 0.44)))
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = wp.sin((0.70 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.38)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.45)
    data[tid] = v0
